              <h2>How the Wales tax calculator works</h2>
              <p>
                This tool estimates your income tax and take‑home pay if you are
                a Welsh taxpayer for the 2024/25 tax year. It combines:
              </p>
              <ul>
                <li>Welsh rates of income tax (set by the Senedd)</li>
