              <h2>Income tax bands for Welsh taxpayers (2024/25)</h2>
              <p>
                Welsh taxpayers pay the same overall income tax rates as the
                rest of the UK on non‑savings, non‑dividend income. The
                difference is that part of the rate is set by the Welsh
                Government.
              </p>

              <div class="formula-box text-sm">
                <strong
                  >Approximate bands used in this calculator (non‑savings,
